column2: SELECT    p.ra,p.dec,f.mjd_i,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.objID,p.err_i,d.thingID FROM    photoObj p  JOIN field f ON p.fieldid=f.fieldid JOIN detectionIndex d ON p.objID=d.objID WHERE    f.mjd_i != #   /*AND p.psfMag_i - p.cmodelMag_i > #*/   AND p.ra BETWEEN # AND #   AND p.dec BETWEEN -.# AND -.#
